headline.main: 1 Dead, 2 Injured in Police Chase Following Carjacking
headline.print_headline: 1 Dead, 2 Injured in Police Chase Following Carjacking

lead_paragraph: Police say a carjacking suspect is dead and two others injured after crashing into a utility pole during a police chase in Louisville.
